@startuml
title LockHandle 租约句柄生命周期图

legend right
  [DOC: FlowNode]      说明性状态，不进入代码枚举
  [CODE: RuntimeFlag]  LockRuntimeState 中的 lost/released
  [CODE: Provider]     Provider 返回结果
endlegend

[*] --> HELD

HELD : [DOC: FlowNode]\n创建 LockHandle 后的默认状态\nlost=false\nreleased=false

HELD --> HELD : checkHeld success
HELD --> HELD : renew success\nLockRenewStatus=RENEWED

HELD --> LOST : renew NOT_FOUND / NOT_OWNER
HELD --> LOST : checkHeld false
HELD --> LOST : release NOT_FOUND / NOT_OWNER

LOST : [CODE: RuntimeFlag]\nlost=true

HELD --> RELEASED : unlock success\nLockReleaseStatus=RELEASED
RELEASED : [CODE: RuntimeFlag]\nreleased=true

HELD --> PROVIDER_ERROR_STATE : renew/check/release provider error
PROVIDER_ERROR_STATE : [DOC: FlowNode]\nProvider 异常\n不确定是否失锁

PROVIDER_ERROR_STATE --> HELD : later checkHeld success
PROVIDER_ERROR_STATE --> LOST : later checkHeld false
PROVIDER_ERROR_STATE --> RELEASED : later unlock success

LOST --> LOST : checkHeld false
LOST --> RELEASED_AFTER_LOST : unlock called\nmarkReleasedOnce()

RELEASED_AFTER_LOST : [CODE: RuntimeFlag]\nlost=true\nreleased=true

RELEASED --> RELEASED : duplicate unlock\nmarkReleasedOnce=false\nno-op
RELEASED --> RELEASED : renew returns false
RELEASED --> RELEASED : checkHeld returns false

RELEASED_AFTER_LOST --> RELEASED

RELEASED --> [*]
LOST --> [*]

note bottom of LOST
  LOST 不一定代表业务已经停止。
  它只表示当前 LockHandle 已经被判断为不再持有锁。
end note

note bottom of RELEASED
  RELEASED 表示本地释放逻辑已经执行过。
  通过 released.compareAndSet(false, true)
  保证同一个 handle 只释放一次。
end note

@enduml